757
00:54:26,263 --> 00:54:27,097
Selamat jalan.

758
00:54:30,725 --> 00:54:32,686
- Syukurlah dah selesai.
- Betul.

759
00:54:35,855 --> 00:54:37,524
- Saya yakin pasti berjaya.
- Ya.

760
00:54:40,360 --> 00:54:41,736
- Oh, ya. Gun-woo.
- Apa?

761
00:54:42,237 --> 00:54:43,697
Ingat lagi Presiden Choi

762
00:54:44,239 --> 00:54:46,658
pernah tanya Im tentang jongkong emas?

763
00:54:47,492 --> 00:54:50,954
Ya. Menurut dia, orang bernama
In-beom sahaja tahu lokasinya.

764
00:54:51,037 --> 00:54:51,871
Betul.

765
00:54:51,955 --> 00:54:53,123
Awak rasa, ada berapa?

766
00:54:54,916 --> 00:54:55,750
Entahlah.

767
00:54:56,876 --> 00:54:59,087
Saya rasa, tentu ada berpuluh bilion.

768
00:55:00,964 --> 00:55:01,798
Wah…

769
00:55:03,383 --> 00:55:05,969
Termasuk duit yang dicuri
daripada mendiang?

770
00:55:06,052 --> 00:55:06,886
Betul.

771
00:55:07,595 --> 00:55:09,806
Jika polis gagal berkas Kim,

772
00:55:10,974 --> 00:55:12,642
dia akan lari ke luar negara

773
00:55:13,601 --> 00:55:14,853
bersama duit itu.

774
00:55:16,062 --> 00:55:16,980
Tak boleh jadi.

775
00:55:17,647 --> 00:55:18,773
Itu milik mendiang.

776
00:55:19,607 --> 00:55:20,442
Jom bersiap sedia.

777
00:55:21,151 --> 00:55:23,445
Kita buru dan belasah dia sampai mati.

778
00:55:24,154 --> 00:55:24,988
Okey.

779
00:55:32,329 --> 00:55:33,580
Jom minum sepuasnya!

780
00:55:33,663 --> 00:55:34,622
Ya!

781
00:55:35,165 --> 00:55:38,293
- Beom, Jun-min, syabas!
- Bos!

782
00:55:38,376 --> 00:55:41,212
Okey, pusingan kedua di rumah saya!

783
00:55:43,673 --> 00:55:44,632
Kenapa?

784
00:55:45,592 --> 00:55:46,885
Awak tak bau apa-apa?

785
00:55:47,969 --> 00:55:49,012
Eun-seo, kenapa?

786
00:55:49,596 --> 00:55:51,556
Macam ada bau terbakar.

787
00:55:53,892 --> 00:55:55,477
Hei, diam.

788
00:55:59,439 --> 00:56:00,273
Jangan.

789
00:56:18,124 --> 00:56:20,335
Celaka!

790
00:56:27,842 --> 00:56:29,302
Baliklah.

791
00:56:33,807 --> 00:56:35,558
PARK JUN-HO, KIM SEOK-YEON, LEE DU-YEONG
SHIN MYEONG-JA, YOON CHANG-WON

792
00:56:35,642 --> 00:56:36,476
HWANG YANG-JUNG

793
00:56:37,185 --> 00:56:38,395
CHOI TAE-HO

794
00:56:58,456 --> 00:56:59,541
Kau di mana?

795
00:56:59,624 --> 00:57:00,667
Masih di pejabat.

796
00:57:01,251 --> 00:57:03,711
Pemandu aku akan hantar sebuah telefon.

797
00:57:04,462 --> 00:57:05,964
Aku nak kau cari orang.

798
00:57:06,047 --> 00:57:07,382
Berapa orang?

799
00:57:07,465 --> 00:57:09,050
Seorang lelaki tua.

800
00:57:09,634 --> 00:57:10,468
Perlu segera?

801
00:57:10,969 --> 00:57:12,637
Cari sebelum tengah hari esok,

802
00:57:13,555 --> 00:57:15,098
aku bayar tiga kali ganda.

803
00:57:16,683 --> 00:57:17,725
Baiklah.

804
00:57:17,809 --> 00:57:22,689
JABATAN SIASATAN JENAYAH BERAT
UNIT 1

805
00:59:05,375 --> 00:59:08,336
Terjemahan sari kata oleh:

